                     Names of individuals who were probably original commissioners are mentioned
                     in some supplication formulas,
                      <persName ref="PRS13323GabraSellase">Gabra Śǝllāse</persName> (<locus target="#6ra #6rb #136ra #150rc"/>) and

                     <persName ref="PRS13327WaldaMaryam">Walda Māryām</persName> (<locus target="#24rb #91rb #144vb"/>).
